_sText:
Unzip the file .rar into your cstrike\Maps directory


Example:

C:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\YourEmail\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Thanks to Pepe for helping me.
And thanks to TopHATTwaffle for his textures. Always very nice...
